WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:05.000
Big Buck Bunny is resting on the grass.

00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:10.000
A butterfly flies in and lands on Bunny's nose.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Bunny smiles happily, watching the butterfly.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Three small animals emerge from the forest.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Frank the flying squirrel leads the group.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:30.000
They begin to bully Bunny.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.000
Bunny's butterfly friend is in danger.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.000
An angry Bunny prepares to fight back.

00:00:41.000 --> 00:00:45.000
Bunny starts building elaborate traps.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:50.000
The small animals fall into the traps one by one.

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Frank finally gets caught in a trap too.

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:00.000
Peace returns and Bunny smiles again.
